=========

ChatGPT API is an interface that allows developers to integrate ChatGPT into their applications. 
It uses a Large Language Model (LLM) that has been pre-trained on vast amounts of text data. 
The model understands natural language and can generate human-like responses for tasks 
such as question answering, translation, summarization, and content generation.

